            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1949-01-05T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1947-05-04T17:00:00-05:00" n="689" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d689">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>In telegram 122, March 17, 1948, to Belgrade, repeated to Sofia, Bucharest,
                    Budapest, Moscow, Rome, Paris, and London, the Department of State set forth the
                    ultimate United States objectives toward the Balkan states, including
                    Yugoslavia. For the text of the telegram, see <ref target="#pg_312">page
                        312</ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
